<paragraph blockId="2.[189,1210,2021,2084]" box="[189,933,2021,2047]" pageId="2" pageNumber="197">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[189,323,2021,2047]" pageId="2" pageNumber="197">Phenology:</emphasis>
—Flowering and fruiting late September into October.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
